<h2>ECON 159: <strong>Game Theory</strong> </h2>
<table id="lectureHeader" summary="lecture header" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
	<tr>
		<td width="510" nowrap="nowrap">
			<span id="lectureNum">Lecture 13 - </span>
			<span id="lectureName">Sequential games: moral hazard, incentives, and hungry lions</span></td>
		<td width="248" id="lectureNav" nowrap="nowrap">
			<span id="backNav"><a href="midterm_exam.html">&lt;&lt; previous session</a></span>
			<span id="navPipe">|</span>
